<p>
  Mastodon is a decentralized, sleek microblogging website for absolute beginners to the fediverse,
  which offers a familiar design.
</p>

<p>
  My account boosts cat pictures, art, and generally dumb stuff that I find funny or interesting.
  I also express my feelings and opinions over multiple topics, including software development. 
